{"tid":1331106,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（社運進化 深度學習）第十人理論","createTime":"2019-07-18T22:53:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T23:31:19.000Z","uid":263218,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"193cb1e546a33204e8accd5e7ab2bb4a315cc101","tid":1331106,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T22:53:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">第十人理論</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n看過末日Z戰的人一定知道，前聯合國調查員藍恩&middot;傑瑞在以色列的耶路撒冷見了尤爾根&middot;汪布朗，尤爾根&middot;汪布朗當時說過了一句話:「當第十個人」，究竟這個當第十個人的意思是什麼呢?來源又是從哪裡來的呢?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在1973年第四次中東戰爭後，以色列國防部專門成立一個機構，稱為「Red Team」，號稱是魔鬼代言人，他們可以運用各種方式挑戰情報單位做出的普遍假設，用來保證情報的準確性。這個機構就是那第十人，不管前九個人的結論看起來有多正確多萬無一失，搭們還是得提出異議，找出這九個人都錯的特例，並提供軍方進行評測。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這個機構的特點就是小而精，所有成員都具有學術背景，最重要的一點是可以不受限制的訪問各類訊息，上可抵將軍，下可達士兵，他們收集並分析各類的訊息，找出信息環節上的漏洞和錯誤，挑戰一切的假設和判斷。他們的信條不是「He who dares wins(勇敢者才能贏)」，而是「He who thinks,wins(善於思考者贏)」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這就是以色列的「Intelligence reforms(情報改革)」法則，後稱為「第十人理論」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第十人理論對於任何議題來講，這種理論可以挑出他人的錯誤，並加強改善，這樣就能使防護更加完美。有一句話說:「一分預防勝過十分治療」。只要能接近完美的防護，就能阻止可怕的事情發生。"},{"pid":"1ca8f90daaab37203d53d828f05f83da1ccf9fea","tid":1331106,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T22:54:09.000Z","msg":"Source : <a href=\"https://hg2068zhggfxo.pixnet.net/blog/post/202742329-第十人理論\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhg2068zhggfxo.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F202742329-%E7%AC%AC%E5%8D%81%E4%BA%BA%E7%90%86%E8%AB%96&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDVJiVKGJ8LWvq%2BeQg4NrPGo%3D&h=18ae8fc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hg2068zhggfxo.pixnet.net/blog/post/202742329-第十人理論</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae5bbd4ff4e2b20aa503d67df0340e08e6f0804","tid":1331106,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T22:55:58.000Z","msg":"21/7 兄弟爬山 安全為上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c1532b12104cfe704ce60620c997c77a0db3050","tid":1331106,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T22:57:05.000Z","msg":"向以色列學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"130492be61ee98f9d379b96148284681523c7302","tid":1331106,"uid":263218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T23:13:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點解要向以色列學習</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">首先，以色列雖然仆街霸左人好多地方，但你唔能否認佢係一個相當有智慧的國家，香港要學習成功地方的經驗</span>。以色列🇮🇱由沒有政府到建立自己的政府，用左好多年時間，但佢地冇放棄，反而識得把握大勢，成功爭取立國。海外的港人不妨參考猶太人的做法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">其次，以色列能夠係中東地區生存打滾，有一套應付惡鄰的技巧，猶如香港都位於惡鄰一旁</span>。由外交策略到軍事武裝，以色列贏得七日戰爭，到現在能發揮自己的地緣政治定位。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n岩岩訓醒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4cd9b1a42ce36d7c3c7a4aa588069d664a0c50","tid":1331106,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T23:15:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b1aa50f9255bdb2ce671d01d5dcebde82aa9967","tid":1331106,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T23:17:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/以色列历史\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E4%BB%A5%E8%89%B2%E5%88%97%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDVJiVKGJ8LWvq%2BeQg4NrPGo%3D&h=a8998597\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/以色列历史</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n得閒睇下維基"},{"pid":"f0c3f19648c9158b31228ec4256380200e0a08c8","tid":1331106,"uid":274911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T23:18:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等我為大家回憶下決定721去定唔去<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1324531/page/5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1324531/page/5</a><br />\n<br />\n[721] 和理非之所以企出嚟 唔係想勇武以死相博 而係想大家一齊凱旋歸來<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dkBgNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dkBgNS</a><br />\n<br />\n[7.21] 同我推返哂721上熱門<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dkeybS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dkeybS</a><br />\n<br />\n【香城OL wiki】史上最全攻略！！持續更新！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dkgKdS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dkgKdS</a>"},{"pid":"9db57df9f9b194d51daba6a1ec1959c4c3f7574b","tid":1331106,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T23:28:11.000Z","msg":"早晨呀 香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5af45d30010e363a76721e3e2fd485c87475e1f","tid":1331106,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T23:29:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9eec694e65005e9f70053083b9457e87c0e15b8","tid":1331106,"uid":260793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T23:31:19.000Z","msg":"香港早晨"}]}